Revision history for Perl extension Term-ANSIColor-Concise

3.02 2026-01-19T10:11:49Z

    - Fix luminance setting to reduce chroma when out of RGB gamut
    - Fix typo in luv method (as_Lab -> as_Luv)
    - Improve documentation for effect codes

3.01 2025-09-05T09:44:27Z

    - Add support for color adjustment modifiers: luminance (y), lightness (l), saturation (s), hue (h)
    - Add support for color transformation operations: complement (c), LCH hue rotation (r), inversion (i)
    - Add support for grayscale conversion: luminance-based (g) and lightness-based (G)
    - Add support for HSL, LCH, and Lab color space specifications
    - Add comprehensive documentation and test coverage for new color features
    - Fix grammar and language issues throughout documentation

2.08 2024-11-16T05:38:13Z

    - add "Left Right Margin Mode" sequence
    - treat nul, vt, np, U+2028, U+2029 as EOL

2.07 2024-09-12T01:19:56Z

    - support CPR and STBM sequence
    - implement csi_report() function

2.06 2024-05-09T08:40:54Z

    - now ansi_color() returns result list in array context

2.05 2023-06-17T08:18:50Z

    - introduce cumulative color policy

2.04 2023-06-16T10:07:55Z

    - support other sequences:
        VPA, VPR, CSI, OSC, DECEC, DECDC

2.03 2023-06-06T02:54:05Z

    - support some additional CSI names:
        Insert/Delete/Erase Character (ICH, DCH, ECH)
        Insert/Delete Line (IL, DL)

2.0201 2023-03-15T10:56:15Z

    - fix typo bug introduced in 2.02

2.02 2023-03-15T10:07:07Z

    - produce color sequence after CR char (bug fix)

2.01 2022-08-24T07:53:46Z

    - version 2.01

2.00_05 2022-08-23T10:00:03Z

    - try not to index local package

2.00_04 2022-08-22T09:33:25Z

    - require Graphics::ColorNames@v3

2.00_03 2022-08-19T11:55:59Z

    - improve COLOR NAMES section

2.00_02 2022-08-19T01:16:31Z

    - deprecate V effect
    - improve document

2.00_01 2022-08-15T02:13:55Z

    - export cached_ansi_color()

2.00_00 2022-08-13T06:20:58Z

    - Spin off from Getopt::EX::Colomap

